parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vacuum pump can cause the gear to explode, damaging the camshaft and potentially leading to a loss of vehicle control, which can result in accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
